T1  - The power problems of unit root test in time series with autoregressive errors
AU  - DeJong, David N.
AU  - Nankervis, John C.
AU  - Savin, N.E.
AU  - Whiteman, Charles H.
JO  - Journal of Econometrics
VL  - 53
